(fn fibonacci
  [n]
  (if (> n 1)
    (let [prev (fibonacci (- n 1))
          Fsum (fn sum
                 [s]
                 (if (nil? (first (rest s)))
                   (first s)
                   (+ (first s)
                      (sum (rest s)))))
          Ftail (fn tail
                  [s n]
                  (if (or (= (count s) n) (< (count s) n))
                    s
                    (tail (rest s)
                          n)))]
      (conj prev (Fsum (Ftail prev 2))))
    [1]))

( partial ( fn make-fib [ cseq tsize ]
  ( if ( = 0 tsize )
    []
    ( if ( = ( count cseq ) tsize )
      cseq
      ( let [ seqCount (count cseq) ]
	      ( cond
	        ( = seqCount 0 ) ( make-fib [ 1 ] tsize )
	        ( = seqCount 1 ) ( make-fib [ 1 1 ] tsize )
	        :else ( make-fib ( conj cseq ( apply + ( take-last 2 cseq ) ) ) tsize )))))) [] )
